verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
Holy, holy, holy Lord,
God of power and might,
heaven and earth are full,
are full of your glory.

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
Holy, holy, holy Lord,
God of power and might,
heaven and earth are full,
are full of your glory.

verse.name: v3
verse.lines:
Blessed is the one who comes
in the name of the Lord!
Hosanna in the highest!
Hosanna in the highest!
Hosanna in the highest!
Hosanna in the highest!
